{
  "stem": "2684.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Then we ran back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Then he came 4 o'clock up, whatever we were covered with, not much.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I don't know what the cover was-- a blanket, or just the remnants of a blanket.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then he said, you have to go to the toilet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I said, we don't have to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Yes, you have to.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then you had to go out, and you have to put on your things, the stripe.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Mostly we slept in the stripe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But sometimes it wasn't allowed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "When he was in a bad mood, it was not allowed to sleep in the stripe.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Then he sent us out to the toilet in the night, 4 o'clock the morning in the-- in the winter because that was already winter up there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "That was October, November.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Anyway, the culmination of the whole lager is that so few people left after, after September, October, November.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Beginning of December, they have to evacuate the lager because there wasn't enough people to work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They then brought new ones.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About 200 of us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't count one by one, but approximately 200 because I don't think so we needed more than two wagon to take us wherever they evacuated us.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Later on, I knew we were taken to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So from here, they shipped us to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we arrived in Dachau at night time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By freight train.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Again, filled up the train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was already a little bit-- [LAUGHS] a little bit down on my physique-- the, the well-built guy become a, a walking skeleton, but still had muscles, and I still had energy.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I was approximately 35 kilos.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wouldn't know because they didn't ship them with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't come with us in the-- in the wagon.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
